    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f3cd5d87a55759bf3ae9481990fd70f3.poster.avif?t=1768516713\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f3cd5d87a55759bf3ae9481990fd70f3.webm?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f3cd5d87a55759bf3ae9481990fd70f3.mp4?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏介绍:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;塞西尔惊魂&quot; 是一段令人毛骨悚然、充满悬疑的体验，让你时刻紧张不已。加入约翰和莎拉的行列，踏上前往神秘诡异的塞西尔酒店的浪漫假期之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，当他们入睡后，他们的梦想假期变成了一场噩梦。约翰醒来时发现自己被锁在一个黑暗的牢房里。他努力寻找出路时，意识到莎拉失踪了，他必须在为时已晚之前找到她. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏特色</strong>:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/aa105d2b3f59ce787dd7c3dd03c0df19.poster.avif?t=1768516713\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/aa105d2b3f59ce787dd7c3dd03c0df19.webm?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/aa105d2b3f59ce787dd7c3dd03c0df19.mp4?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>第一人称视角:</strong></u> 以约翰的视角，在黑暗的走廊中经历一场又一场令人脊背发凉的恐怖追逐战，真实地感受紧张刺激的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/2fc12d53786ee976fab9373334073ec3.poster.avif?t=1768516713\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/2fc12d53786ee976fab9373334073ec3.webm?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/2fc12d53786ee976fab9373334073ec3.mp4?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>恐怖诡异的敌人:</strong></u> 探索塞西尔酒店的走廊，近距离接触令人毛骨悚然的怪物和巨型金属异形，要时刻小心每一个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/3d3df3ce3640937a15bc973d98816b66.poster.avif?t=1768516713\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/3d3df3ce3640937a15bc973d98816b66.webm?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/3d3df3ce3640937a15bc973d98816b66.mp4?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>沉浸式游戏体验:</strong></u> 用手中的枪与敌人交锋，探索危险的房间，利用环境中的物品穿越塞西尔酒店的谜之走廊并逃脱命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f24b0b02799a58f98e3f6b39097e3db1.poster.avif?t=1768516713\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f24b0b02799a58f98e3f6b39097e3db1.webm?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2019340/extras/f24b0b02799a58f98e3f6b39097e3db1.mp4?t=1768516713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>解谜与探索:</strong></u> 解开紧张刺激的谜题，利用一路上的发现开启新的区域，同时揭开这个神秘酒店的来龙去脉。</p>",
